WEBVTT

01:55:19.941 --> 01:55:21.399
-Oh, and Georgekutty...
-Yes?

01:55:21.483 --> 01:55:23.149
We'll do all the shopping
in Ernakulam.

01:55:23.233 --> 01:55:24.608
Why go all the way to Ernakulam?

01:55:24.649 --> 01:55:26.191
Don't we have good shops
in Thodupuzha?

01:55:26.233 --> 01:55:27.899
No, we have to go to Ernakulam.
